# loombox relay - Caddy site block for prodbox's /etc/caddy/Caddyfile.
# Caddy terminates TLS (auto Let's Encrypt) and reverse-proxies to the
# loopback-published relay container. reverse_proxy passes WebSocket upgrades
# through automatically, which the relay's /ws endpoint needs.
#
# Requires: DNS A record relay.loombox.dev -> prodbox public IP (DNS-only /
# grey cloud so Caddy, not Cloudflare, manages the cert), and 80/443 open (UFW).

relay.loombox.dev {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:5185
}
